commit_message:
Added GUI

GUI is not (currently) as functional as command line:
- Cannot select AA output (1 or 3).
- Cannot detect start/stop codon.

Fixed bug with RNA input sequence

Used to raise error when given RNA input.

Bug fixes, improved output

- Fixed bugs with transcription and translation
- Output mRNA is always 5' -> 3'
- Shows coding and template DNA strand with polarity.

Added examples to README.md

Tested all functionality of the program and updated accordingly.
